item.title: A quarter has gone by at Amazon
item.description: Time flies. And in this short time - I completed my first quarter at AWS, and it is still #Day1. Needless to say - it has been a roller-coaster ride. I am part of Professional Services team here, and we provide assistance to our customers through a collection of offerings which helps achieve specific outcomes related to enterprise cloud adoption.
